micro-style.css
===============

Minimal, simple, tunable style for your websites.

Author:  Giovanni Santini
Mail:    giovanni.santini@proton.me
License: MIT


Usage
-----

To use this stylesheet, include the following in your <head>:

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://san7o.github.io/micro-style.css/micro-style.css" />

Examples
--------

  https://san7o.github.io/kivebpf/
  https://san7o.github.io/micro-headers/
  https://san7o.github.io/haplolang/
  https://san7o.github.io/micro-draw.h/